HEADWORD: Curb roof
<hw>Curb" roof`</hw> <pr>(r??f`)</pr>. <def>A roof having a double
slope, or composed, on each side, of two parts which have unequal
inclination; a gambrel roof.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>curbside</ent>⟦br⟧
